    "Semi-hermetic lead-lined sliding doors are specialized access solutions designed for radiology departments and diagnostic imaging rooms where both radiation protection and basic environmental control are required. These doors integrate a high-density lead core for effective radiation attenuation with a robust, gasket-sealed frame that minimizes dust ingress and air leakage. By balancing reliable shielding with a smooth, easy-to-sanitize surface, they provide a practical and safe entry point for clinical areas where the extreme pressure differentials of a fully hermetic system are not strictly necessary.",
